        <h2>Competition Categories</h2>

        <h3>Classic Lashes</h3>
        <p>Judging criteria:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Precise isolation and placement</li>
          <li>Uniform curl and direction</li>
          <li>Proper lash-to-extension ratio</li>
          <li>Clean adhesive application</li>
          <li>Symmetry between eyes</li>
          <li>Overall aesthetic appeal</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Volume Lashes</h3>
        <p>Advanced technical requirements:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Perfect fan creation and consistency</li>
          <li>Proper fan placement and angle</li>
          <li>Density and fullness</li>
          <li>No stickies or clumping</li>
          <li>Wispy, fluffy appearance</li>
          <li>Artistic design and mapping</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Mega Volume</h3>
        <p>The ultimate technical challenge:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>10D-16D fan creation</li>
          <li>Extreme density without weight</li>
          <li>Perfect separation</li>
          <li>Dramatic but wearable result</li>
          <li>Speed and precision combined</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Speed Challenges</h3>
        <p>Race against the clock:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Complete full set in limited time (60-90 minutes)</li>
          <li>Quality cannot be sacrificed for speed</li>
          <li>Tests efficiency and technique</li>
          <li>Simulates busy salon conditions</li>
        </ul>

