        <h2>Competition Scoring & Judging</h2>

        <h3>Technical Evaluation</h3>
        <p>Judges assess:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Isolation (25 points):</strong> Each extension on one natural lash</li>
          <li><strong>Placement (20 points):</strong> Proper positioning and angle</li>
          <li><strong>Adhesive (15 points):</strong> Clean application, no excess</li>
          <li><strong>Symmetry (15 points):</strong> Balanced appearance</li>
          <li><strong>Overall Design (25 points):</strong> Aesthetic appeal and artistry</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Disqualifications</h3>
        <p>Common reasons for point deductions or DQ:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Stickies (multiple lashes stuck together)</li>
          <li>Improper isolation</li>
          <li>Damage to natural lashes</li>
          <li>Extensions too heavy or long</li>
          <li>Messy adhesive application</li>
          <li>Uneven or asymmetrical result</li>
        </ul>

